FUNNY MAN raced off the pace on the inside through the opening half mile, continued around the second turn in the four path and was not a threat. CAJUN OCCASION raced in the two path early, continued up the backstretch in the middle of the pack on the outside, navigated the far turn still in the two path and never fired. SCHOOLMASTER (GER) raced in the two path around the first bend, tracked the leader on the inside up the backstretch, saved ground around the far turn and tired in the stretch.
